
# MySQL Practice Repository

Welcome to the MySQL Practice Repository  
This repository is maintained by [shovo896](https://github.com/shovo896) and is intended for learning, practicing, and  demonstrating all key concepts of MySQL through real-world examples and SQL scripts.

